@startuml Network_Topology
!theme plain

title Pyroscope Network Topology

cloud "WiFi Network\n10.18.61.0/24" as NETWORK {
    node "WiFi Router\n10.18.61.1" as ROUTER
}

node "Jetson Nano (Robot)\n10.18.61.50" as JETSON {
    component "ROS Master\nroscore\nport 11311" as ROSCORE
    component "Navigation Nodes\n(4 nodes)" as NAV_NODES
    component "Sensor Publishers" as SENSORS
    database "ROS Graph" as ROS_GRAPH

    NAV_NODES --> ROS_GRAPH
    SENSORS --> ROS_GRAPH
    ROSCORE --> ROS_GRAPH : "Manages\ntopics"
}

node "Remote PC (Backend)\n10.18.61.71" as SERVER {
    component "FastAPI Server\n0.0.0.0:8000" as BACKEND_API
    component "ROS Sensor Bridge\n(connects to ROS Master)" as BRIDGE
    database "PostgreSQL\nport 5432" as POSTGRES
    folder "sensor_data/\n(shared files)" as FILES

    BRIDGE --> FILES : "Write"
    BACKEND_API --> FILES : "Read"
    BACKEND_API --> POSTGRES
}

node "Mac (Client)\n10.18.61.100" as MAC {
    component "Web Browser\nlocalhost:5173" as BROWSER
    component "Vite Dev Server\nport 5173" as VITE

    BROWSER --> VITE : "localhost"
}

' Network connections
JETSON -down- ROUTER : "WiFi\n2.4/5 GHz"
SERVER -down- ROUTER : "WiFi or\nEthernet"
MAC -down- ROUTER : "WiFi"

' Application connections
BRIDGE ..> ROSCORE : "ROS Topics\nTCP 11311+\nroscpp"
VITE ..> BACKEND_API : "HTTP REST\nhttp://10.18.61.71:8000\nJSON"
BACKEND_API ..> ROSCORE : "roslaunch\nSSH or\nROS service"

note right of ROSCORE
    **ROS Master**
    - Manages topic publishers/subscribers
    - Runs on Jetson
    - ROS_MASTER_URI exported
      on all ROS nodes
end note

note right of BACKEND_API
    **Backend API**
    - Listens on 0.0.0.0:8000
      (all interfaces)
    - CORS enabled for Mac IP
    - Serves /api/* endpoints
end note

note left of VITE
    **Frontend**
    - Development server
    - Production: static build
      served by nginx
    - API_BASE_URL configured
      to point to 10.18.61.71:8000
end note

legend right
    **Port Summary:**
    | Device | Service | Port |
    | Jetson | ROS Master | 11311+ |
    | Server | FastAPI | 8000 |
    | Server | PostgreSQL | 5432 |
    | Mac | Vite Dev | 5173 |

    **Network Requirements:**
    - All devices on same subnet
    - Static IP recommended for Server
    - Firewall allow ports 8000, 11311
endlegend

@enduml
